      "desc": "Handling of animals.",
      "narrative": "At the time of inspection, there were no attendants monitoring the enclosures that allow members of the public to interact\nwith the animals. In two separate areas, members of the public were seen feeding animals with no attendant present.\nWithout an attendant present to monitor interactions, both animals and members of the public are at greater risk of injury.\nThe facility must have a responsible, knowledgeable, and readily identifiable employee or attendant present at all times\nduring periods of public contact.\nTo be corrected by April 13, 2026.\nThis inspection and exit interview were conducted with a facility representative.\nn"
